tika.dc.description: Fresh off a break-up from a controlling millionaire, Nina Decker is desperate for a new start. She doesn't expect to find it in her former high school teacher, Mr. Aaron Cole. The spark is undeniable - a necessary release from the controlled perfection of their small, affluent town. Unfortunately, Nina's past isn't quite ready to leave her, and it'll stop at nothing to get her back.
